#. Tag: title
#: details-schedules.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deposits"
msgstr "Depósitos"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:62
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "A Deposit is for money coming into your account, such as paychecks, "
#| "bonuses, or interest income."
msgid ""
"These schedules are for money coming into your account, such as a paycheck, "
"bonus, or interest income."
msgstr ""
"É usado um Evento de Depósito para criar um evento recorrente para o "
"dinheiro que entra na sua conta, como o pagamento de um cheque, bónus, "
"ordenados ou receitas de juros."

#. Tag: title
#: details-schedules.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bills/Withdrawals"
msgstr "Contas/Levantamentos"

#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:69
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "A Bill or Withdrawal is for money going out of your account, such as a "
#| "membership, utility bill, taxes, or car registration."
